title: The Glenn Beck Radio Show NOV-25-2013 MON
description:
The Glenn Beck Radio Show NOV-25-2013 MON





The Glenn Beck Program




Listen to The Glenn Beck Radio Program, Monday through Friday, 9am - 12pm ET



        
      
November 25, 2013 11:06 AM



Glenn opens the show discussing the traits of successful people,
        and what describes today's America.

  Also, the hypocrisy of Harry Reid pushing for the nuclear response,
                        when just a short while ago, he was condemning it.

  Plus, the nuclear agreement between Iran and the US,
                          and how Iran got the upper hand,

 and Senator John Cornyn joins the program to answer Glenn's tough questions,

 including why he's against Freedomworks.
